President Donald J. Trump had a phone conversation with Emir Tamim bin Hamad Al Thani of Qatar. They discussed regional developments and ways to strengthen the partnership between the United States and Qatar on security and economic issues. President Trump thanked the Emir for his efforts in countering Iranian destabilizing activities and combating terrorism and extremism. Both leaders emphasized the importance of regional cooperation and a united Gulf Cooperation Council to address regional threats and promote economic prosperity.